{"tid":2034150,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"全新金牛座tg谷（吹水感情）","createTime":"2020-05-25T05:21:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T07:27:41.000Z","uid":217514,"like":7,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d7763f277b6f5fa334bf1b4e81746015dbb90fa7","tid":2034150,"uid":217514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T05:21:40.000Z","msg":"3月開谷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />金牛jj雖然過晒生日<br />\n但都歡迎你地入嚟<br />\n同其他谷冇關係<br />\n<br />\n-有dc群 歡迎大家約埋谷友齊齊入dc一齊打機<br />\n-有得玩tg game 無聊時開下狼人殺<br />\n-有心事台 一齊傾下計可星座角度/普通吹）<br />\n-有聚 自行決定出唔出 冇咩所謂<br />\n<br />\n歡迎曾經入過嘅無限再入 <br />\n但發現入過嘅係唔會加得返 <br />\n所以張form都麻煩你備注返<br />\n會有專人另外搵你<br />\n<br />\n歡迎（非金牛座）嘅人入 <br />\n一齊為你解決溝金牛仔/女嘅難題<br />\n又或者友情上都可以 唔一定要愛情<br />\n<br />\n請記住 未加前都盡量唔好轉tg id，私隱都較返公開<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTg私穩冇較到比任何人加入谷，我係唔會特登Pm你再去加。（你可以係tg設定》私隱同保安〉谷同台》所有人<br />\n<br />\nTg user id:如何設定user id, 設定》編輯個人資料〉用戶名<br />\n<br />\n最後 潛水3日就踢 所以會維持係3日加一次人<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/YKWbL9DVft2VFTNF6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FYKWbL9DVft2VFTNF6&d=g30fgRh1OaLpBbOto8aU3oVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=a81fe7a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/YKWbL9DVft2VFTNF6</a>"},{"pid":"6d8ae789da184e98e2616c197438c131b01d1cd7","tid":2034150,"uid":217514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T07:30:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"289097d1c639d7a17a5eed785447692038df1d7c","tid":2034150,"uid":217514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T12:34:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40090533c016548cc6e99eccd68e072ef077f95d","tid":2034150,"uid":217514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T14:14:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2037f2bae393a2e2838360e9c6407327973bbed3","tid":2034150,"